@startuml
title Timing Diagram - Combat Turn TO-BE

robust "CombatState" as CS
robust "Player" as P
robust "Enemy" as E
concise "UI" as UI

@0
CS is WaitingInput
P is Ready
E is Ready
UI is ShowCombatStatus

@1
UI is ReadCommand
CS is HandleInput

@2
P is Attacking
E is TakingDamage
CS is ResolvePlayerAction

@3
CS is PublishCombatEvent
UI is ShowMessage

@4
E is Attacking
P is TakingDamage
CS is ResolveEnemyAction

@5
CS is CheckStateTransition
UI is RefreshCombatStatus

@enduml